attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles a stool. First, the instructor tells him to disassemble it; the student untightens the middle screw and four screws. He then disassembles four screws, disassembles the seat; then unscrews the middle screw, and finally disassembles the legs.

attributes.Transcription: Hello, thank you for agreeing to take part in our study. In front of you, you will see a stool from ikea.
Your task for now will be to please disassemble it, you may now begin.
